#: src/concepts/architecture.md:9
msgid ""
"**Dataflow-oriented**: Applications are directed graphs of nodes connected "
"by typed data channels. Nodes declare inputs and outputs; the framework "
"handles routing, scheduling, and lifecycle."
msgstr ""

#: src/concepts/architecture.md:10
msgid ""
"**Zero-copy performance**: Messages above 4 KiB use shared memory with "
"128-byte aligned buffers and atomic coordination, achieving 10-17x lower "
"latency than ROS2."
msgstr ""

#: src/concepts/architecture.md:11
msgid ""
"**Multi-language**: First-class support for Rust, Python (PyO3), C, and C++ "
"nodes — all sharing the same Apache Arrow data format."
msgstr ""

#: src/concepts/architecture.md:12
msgid ""
"**Four-layer stack**: Message protocol, core libraries, daemon/runtime "
"execution, and CLI/coordinator orchestration."
