#: src/concepts/types.md:139
msgid "`dora validate` and `dora build` check:"
msgstr ""

#: src/concepts/types.md:141
msgid ""
"**Key existence**: `output_types` keys must appear in `outputs`, "
"`input_types` keys must appear in `inputs`"
msgstr ""

#: src/concepts/types.md:142
msgid ""
"**URN resolution**: All type URNs must exist in the standard or user-defined "
"type library. Typos get \"did you mean?\" suggestions."
msgstr ""

#: src/concepts/types.md:143
msgid ""
"**Edge compatibility**: Connected edges must have compatible types (exact "
"match, implicit widening, or user-defined rules)"
msgstr ""

#: src/concepts/types.md:144
msgid ""
"**Timer auto-typing**: Timer inputs (`dora/timer/*`) are automatically "
"typed as `std/core/v1/UInt64`"
msgstr ""

#: src/concepts/types.md:145
msgid ""
"**Type inference**: When only the upstream side annotates a type, it is "
"inferred on the downstream input and reported"
msgstr ""

#: src/concepts/types.md:146
msgid "**Parameterized types**: Parameter mismatches are detected (see above)"
msgstr ""

#: src/concepts/types.md:147
msgid ""
"**Metadata patterns**: `output_metadata` keys and `pattern` shorthands are "
"validated (see below)"
msgstr ""

#: src/concepts/types.md:148
msgid ""
"**Schema compatibility**: Struct types are checked at the field level -- "
